                <h2>Who is This Stream For?</h2>
                <p>
                    The Skilled Worker stream is for individuals who have
                    received a job offer in a skilled occupation (NOC TEER 0, 1,
                    2, or 3) and have several years of experience in that field.
                    Unlike the International Graduate stream, you do <strong
                        >not</strong
                    > need a recent Canadian degree.
                </p>
                <p>This stream is ideal if you:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Have 2+ years of work experience in your field</li>
                    <li>
                        Hold a job offer from a BC employer in a skilled
                        occupation
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Don't have a recent Canadian degree but want to
                        immigrate
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Are already working in BC and want to transition to PR
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Have strong work experience but moderate language scores
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Core Eligibility Requirements</h2>
                <p>
                    To qualify for the <strong
                        >BC PNP Skills Immigration - Skilled Worker</strong
                    > stream, you must meet ALL of the following requirements:
                </p>

                <h3>1. Valid Job Offer</h3>
                <div
                    class="bg-slate-50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-4 not-prose"
                >
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-green-600">✓</span> Full-time position
                            (30+ hours per week)
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-green-600">✓</span> Indeterminate/permanent
                            (no end date)
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-green-600">✓</span> From an eligible
                            BC employer
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-green-600">✓</span> In a skilled occupation
                            (TEER 0, 1, 2, or 3)
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-green-600">✓</span> Work location is
                            in British Columbia
                        </li>
                    </ul>
