                <h3>2. Wage Standards</h3>
                <p>
                    The offered wage must be competitive with BC market rates
                    for the occupation. BC PNP checks wages against Job Bank
                    data. Significantly below-median wages raise red flags about
                    job offer legitimacy.
                </p>
