                <h3>3. Directly Related Work Experience</h3>
                <p>
                    You must have at least <strong
                        >2 years of full-time work experience</strong
                    > that is directly related to the job offer. This is the #1 reason
                    for Skilled Worker refusals.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-100 my-8 not-prose"
                >
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-purple-900 text-lg mb-2">
                        What Counts as "Directly Related"?
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-purple-800 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Your 2 years of experience must generally be in the <strong
                            >same NOC code</strong
                        > as the BC job offer.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <div class="font-bold text-green-700 text-sm mb-2">
                                ✓ Usually Acceptable
                            </div>
                            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
                                <li>• Same NOC code</li>
                                <li>• Higher-level position in same field</li>
                                <li>
                                    • Closely related NOC in same job family
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
                            <div class="font-bold text-red-700 text-sm mb-2">
                                ✗ Usually Not Acceptable
                            </div>
                            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
                                <li>• Different field entirely</li>
                                <li>• Lower-skill-level role</li>
                                <li>• Unrelated duties</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
